data.description: $5000 INCENTIVE TO BUYER TO USE AS THEY WISH - TOWARD CLOSING AND OR RATE BUYDOWNS!  Bring the large family to this 4BR, 2.5BA featuring open floor plan and main level master suite.  Kitchen w/island, pantry & refrigerator, laminate floors throughout and tile in wet areas, large bonus on main level used to be garage and could be converted back, master w/full bath w/his and her vanities, walk in closet, garden tub and separate shower, 3 additional bedrooms up are spacious, covered front and back porches, privacy fenced yard, detached storage, award winning school system, possible ZERO DOWN on this one too!!
